commit.message:
DOCS: Update API description for "Runner Operation".

* Provide description Gherkin grammar containments
* Add description for Rule(s).
FIX: Cross-reference problem (copy+paste) in Rule class docstring.

Clarify select-by-name uses regex pattern (related to: issue #810)

Clarifiy select-by-name uses regex pattern:

* Adapt command-line option --name help text
* Update command-line args docs for behave
Gherkin parser: Cleanups related to question in #800 (ParseError usage)
docs: parse_expression, add links to parse_type module and CardinalityField support.
docs: Rename page 'parse_expressions' (was: parse_builtin_types) and update table to current parse-1.12.1

CLEANUP: Add ContextMode enum related to #797

Add ContextMode enum to cleanup weirdness related to issue #797.
Pre-existing Context.BEHAVE/USER constants overshadowed user attributes
in Context.attribute retrieval case.
pytest: Disable DeprecatedWarning from distutils package.
Add basic feature-test for wildcard pattern-matching that is supported by cucumber-tag-expressions (python-only).
Tweak pytest configuration to silence JUnit XML dialect warning.

Merge pull-request #767 with minor tweaks.
FIX: use_fixture_by_tag didn't return the actual fixture in all cases.
